<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390465>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Photographs of male (A–C) and female (D–G) of Microcyba oromia n. sp., paratypes from Eth019. A, D, habitus, dorsal view; B, same, lateral view; C, prosoma, frontal view; E, F, opisthosoma, ventral view, different specimens; G, epigynum, ventral view. Scale bars: A–F, 0.5mm; G, 0.1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390465/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8390467>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Details of male palpal structure (A–E) and female epigynum (F, G) of Microcyba oromia n. sp., paratypes from Eth010. A, B, right palp, retrolateral and prolateral view, respectively; C, distal part of palp, retrolateral view; D, tibia, and paracymbium, prolateral view; E, tibia, dorsal view; F, G, epigynum, ventral and dorsal view, respectively. Scale bar: 0.1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8390467/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

